data.eml:eml: Amblyceps cerinum, a new catfish (Teleostei: Amblycipitidae) from northeastern India

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ng, Heok Hee, Wright, Jeremy J. (2010): Amblyceps cerinum, a new catfish (Teleostei: Amblycipitidae) from northeastern India. Zootaxa 2672: 50-60, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.199168
